	a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ChristianLiterature> , <https://betamasaheft.eu/Homily> , <https://betamasaheft.eu/Translation> , <https://betamasaheft.eu/MonasticLiterature> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "Dǝrsān za-anbaro\n                                                  labāse ʾAmlāk walda ʾabaw ḥawāryāt ʾeṗṗis qoṗṗosāt\n                                                  bǝḍuʿ ʾabbā ʾAtnāsyos baṭrǝyārk za-ʾƎlla\n                                                  ʾƎskǝndǝryā za-darasa ba-ʿǝlata tazkāru la-bǝʾsi\n                                                  nabiy mamhǝra ḥǝgg za-manakosāt ʾabbā Ṗākʷǝmis\n                                                  ʾaba māḫbarāt" , "ድርሳን፡ ዘአንበሮ፡ ለባሴ፡ አምላክ፡ ወልደ፡ አበው፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳት፡ ብፁዕ፡ አባ፡ አትናስዮስ፡ በጥርያርክ፡ ዘእለ፡ እስክንድርያ፡\n            ዘደረሰ፡ በዕለተ፡ ተዝካሩ፡ ለብእሲ፡ ነቢይ፡ መምህረ፡ ሕግ፡ ዘመነኮሳት፡ አባ፡ ጳኵሚስ፡ አበ፡ ማኅበራት፡"@gez ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P102_has_title> <https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1628Homily%2Ftitle%2Ft1> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "Dǝrsān za-anbaro labāse ʾAmlāk walda ʾabaw ḥawāryāt\n            ʾeṗṗis qoṗṗosāt bǝḍuʿ ʾabbā ʾAtnāsyos baṭrǝyārk za-ʾƎlla ʾƎskǝndǝryā za-darasa ba-ʿǝlata tazkāru la-bǝʾsi nabiy\n          mamhǝra ḥǝgg za-manakosāt ʾabbā Ṗākʷǝmis ʾaba māḫbarāt"@gez , "Homily on Pachomius"@en ;
